<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Playfair Display' rel='stylesheet'>
    <title>Homepage</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
      }

      html {
        display:flex;
        justify-content: center;
        background-color: #212529;
        font-family: 'Playfair Display';
        height: 100%;
      }

      body {
        width: 1300px;
      }

      a:link, a:visited,  a:hover, a:active {
        color: #000000;
        text-decoration: none;
      } 

      /* NAV BAR ------------------------------------*/

      nav {
        width: 100%;
        height: 15%;
        background-color: #e9ecef;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #logo {
        display:flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #navItems {
        width: 100%;
        display:flex;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #headerHeader {
        font-size:30px;
        margin:10px;
        margin-right:35px;
      }

      #DumbbellImgHeader {
        width: 70px;
        height: 60%;
        margin:10px;
      }

      /* About ---------------------------------------------- */
      #about {
        display:flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        height: 850px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      #aboutHeader {
        display:flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content:center;
        color: #FFFAFB;
        border-style: solid;
        border-color: #FFFAFB;
        border-width: thick;
        margin: 50px;
        width: 80%;
        height 100%;
        font-size: 25px;
        padding-top: 50px;
        padding-bottom: 50px;
      }

      #aboutContent {
        width: 80%;
        height: 90%;
        color: #e9ecef;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        display:flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 30px;
        border-bottom: solid;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
      }


      /* Hero Img ------------------------------------------- */
      .imgNavigation {
        display:flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content:center;
        align-items:center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      #workoutTrackerHeader, #calorieTrackerHeader {
        display:flex;
        justify-content:center;
        align-items:center;
      }

      #more {
        display:flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content:center;
        color: #FFFAFB;
        border-style: solid;
        border-color: #FFFAFB;
        border-width: thick;
        margin: 50px;
        width: 80%;
        height 100%;
        font-size: 25px;
        padding-top: 50px;
        padding-bottom: 50px;
      }

      #other {
        display:flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content:center;
        align-items: center;
        width: 100%;
      }

      #workoutTracker, #calorieTracker {
        display:flex;
        justify-content:center;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-right: 20px;
        padding: 50px;
        border-radius: 15%;
        box-shadow: 5px 5px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        zoom: 0.8
      }

      #workoutTracker {
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)), url('https://i.imgur.com/EA8naGs_d.webp?maxwidth=760&fidelity=grand');
        height: 35vh;
        width: 70%;
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center; 
      }

      #calorieTracker {
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)), url('https://i.imgur.com/TNVBplz_d.webp?maxwidth=760&fidelity=grand');
        height: 35vh;
        width: 70%;
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center; 
      }

      #imgTitles {
        color: #e9ecef;
        border-style: solid;
        border-radius: 15%;
        border-width: thick;
        padding: 20px;
        zoom: 0.8;
      }

      /* Footer --------------------------------------------- */
      #footerContainer {
        background-color:#e9ecef;
        min-height: 10%;
        grid-area:footer;
        display: flex;
        position:relative;
        bottom: 0;
        zoom: 0.78;
      }

      #logoAndName {
        display:flex;
        margin-top: 5px;
        font-size: 15px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #DumbbellImgFooter {
        position:relative;
        top: 0;
        width: 30px;
        height: 20px;
        max-height: 40%;
        margin:10px;
      }

      #copyrightFooter {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 2px;
        font-size:15px;
        margin:10px;
      }

      #linkedinImg {
        position: absolute;
        top:25%;
        right:15px;
        height:55%;
        width:40px;
        max-height: 50px;
        max-width: 50px;
        min-width: 50px;
        min-height: 50px;
      }

      #gitHubImg {
        position: absolute;
        top:15%;
        right:70px;
        width:50px;
        height:70%;
        max-height: 68px;
        max-width: 60px;
        min-width: 60px;
        min-height: 68px;
      }

      @media (min-width:768px)  {
        html {
          min-height: 800px;
        }

        nav {
          font-size: 25px;
        }

        #navItems {
          flex-direction:row;
        }

        #about {
          height: 600px;
        }

        #other {
          flex-direction: row;
          width: 80%;
        }

        #calorieTracker, #workoutTracker {
          height: 50vh;
          width: 50%;
          zoom: 1;
        }


        #footerContainer {
          zoom: 1;
        }
      }

      @media (min-width: 992px) {
        #about {
        }
      }
}

    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- NAV BAR --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->
    <nav>
      <div id="logo">
        <img src="https://i.imgur.com/950J1fr_d.webp?maxwidth=760&fidelity=grand" id="DumbbellImgHeader">
        <h1 id="headerHeader">Workout Planner</h1>
      </div>
      <div id="navItems">
          <p><a href="/homepage"><b style="color:#6c757d;">HOME</b></a></p>
          <p><a href="/homepage/workouts"><b>WORKOUTS</b></a></p>
          <p><a href="/homepage/login"><b>LOGIN</b></a></p>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- ABOUT ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->
    <div id="about">
      <div id="aboutHeader">
        <h1>ABOUT</h1>
      </div>
      <div id="aboutContent">
        <p>
          Want to create workouts? With <b>Workout Planner</b> you are able to create custom workouts and view them whenever you want,
          wherever you want. Simple click on "WORKOUTS" and be redirected to your workouts homepage. From there, you are able to view and create
          your custom workouts. 
        </p>
        <p>
          <b>Workout Planner</b> is a fully functioning C.R.U.D. website created with the ease of use in mind. With its mobile friendly enviroment 
          and easy to use navigation, you can use <b>Workout Planner</b> on the go. Currently, <b>Workout Planner</b> is able to create, read, update, and delete custom workouts using a third party databse (MongoDB). Additionally, a login feature will be added to save your
          workouts within your own profile.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="imgNavigation">
      <div id="more">
        <h1>RELATED</h1>
      </div>
      <div id="other">
        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.muzafferozen.com/workouttracker" id="workoutTracker">
          <div id="workoutTrackerHeader">
            <h1 id="imgTitles">WORKOUT TRACKER</h1>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.muzafferozen.com/calculatorbmi/calculatorbmi" id="calorieTracker">
          <div id="calorieTrackerHeader">
            <h1 id="imgTitles">CALORIE TRACKER</h1>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="footerContainer">
      <div id="footerHeader">
        <div id="logoAndName">
          <img src="https://i.imgur.com/950J1fr_d.webp?maxwidth=760&fidelity=grand" id="DumbbellImgFooter">
          <h1 id="footerHeader">Workout Planner</h1>
          </div>
        <img src="https://i.imgur.com/0hmNIqq_d.webp?maxwidth=760&fidelity=grand" id="linkedinImg" onclick="linkedinButton()">
        <img src="https://i.imgur.com/q4EQ4Me_d.webp?maxwidth=760&fidelity=grand" id="gitHubImg" onclick="gitHubButton()">
        <p id="copyrightFooter">@2022 WorkoutPlanner, M.O. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  <script>
   function linkedinButton() {
      window.open("https://www.linkedin.com/in/muzaffer-ozen/", "_blank").focus();
    }

    function gitHubButton() {
      window.open("https://github.com/TeBossIzHere/WorkoutPlanner", "_blank").focus();
    }
  </script>
</html>
